import React from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux"; import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button"; import Modal from "react-bootstrap/Modal"; import { userprofileStart, userprofileSuccess, userprofileFailed } from "../redux/userSlice"; function Hoso() { const [fullName, setfullName] = useState(""); const [birthDay, setbirthDay] = useState(""); const [gender, setGender] = useState(""); const [bloodgroup, setbloodGroup] = useState(""); const [address, setAddress] = useState(""); const [phone, setPhone] = useState(""); const [email, setEmail] = useState(""); const user = useSelector((state) => state.auth.login.currentUser); const userId = user?._id; const accessToken = user?.accessToken const dispatch = useDispatch(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const userPro = useSelector((state) => state.user.profile.getUser); const [show, setShow] = useState(false); const handleClose = () => setShow(false); const handleShow = () => setShow(true); const [show1, setShow1] = useState(false); const handleClose1 = () => setShow1(false); const handleShow1 = () => setShow1(true); const handleUpdate1 = async () => { const updateUser = { fullName: fullName, birthDay: birthDay, gender: gender, bloodgroup: bloodgroup, }; dispatch(userprofileStart()); try { const response = await fetch("http://localhost:8000/v1/user/profile/"+userId, { method: 'PUT', body: JSON.stringify(updateUser), headers: { token: `Bearer ${accessToken}` } }); if(!response.ok) { dispatch(userprofileFailed()); }else{ const data = await response.json(); dispatch(userprofileSuccess(data)); handleClose; } } catch (error) { dispatch(userprofileFailed()); } } return ( <> <> {/* Navbar Start */}
